#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:4
msgid ":index:`File Variables <variables; file>`"
msgstr ":index:`Bestandsvariabelen <variabelen; bestand>`"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:6
msgid ""
"These variables are populated from information found in the audio files "
"themselves, without any special Picard settings."
msgstr ""
"Deze variabelen worden gevuld met informatie die in de audiobestanden zelf "
"wordt gevonden, zonder specifieke Picard-instellingen."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:10
msgid ""
"Variables that rely on information from the files (e.g.: _bitrate) are only "
"available for use on tracks with attached files, when running scripts "
"manually on files or in the file naming script."
msgstr ""
"Variabelen die afhankelijk zijn van informatie uit de bestanden (zoals "
"_bitrate) kunnen alleen worden gebruikt voor nummers met gekoppelde "
"bestanden, zowel wanneer scripts handmatig worden uitgevoerd als in scripts "
"voor bestandsnamen."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:15
msgid ""
"Prior to version 2.5 Picard did not support using file variables in tagging "
"scripts."
msgstr ""
"Vóór Picard 2.5 werd het gebruik van bestandsvariabelen voor tagscripts niet "
"ondersteund."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:17
msgid "**_bitrate**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:19
msgid "Approximate bitrate in kbps."
msgstr "De geschatte bitsnelheid in kbps."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:21
msgid "**_bits_per_sample**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:23
msgid "Bits of data per sample."
msgstr "Het aantal bits aan data per monster."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:25
msgid "**_channels**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:27
msgid "Number of audio channels in the file."
msgstr "Het aantal audiokanalen in het bestand."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:29
msgid "**_dirname**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:31
msgid ""
"The name of the directory containing the file at the point of being loaded "
"into Picard. (*since Picard 1.1*)"
msgstr ""
"De naam van de map waarin het bestand zich bevond toen het in Picard werd "
"geladen. (*Sinds Picard 1.1.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:33
msgid "**_extension**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:35
msgid "The file's extension. (*since Picard 0.9*)"
msgstr "De bestandsextensie. (*Sinds Picard 0.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:37
msgid "**_filename**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:39
msgid "The name of the file without extension. (*since Picard 1.1*)"
msgstr "De naam van het bestand, zonder de extensie. (*Sinds Picard 1.1.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:41
msgid "**_file_created_timestamp**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:43
msgid ""
"The file creation timestamp in the form 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS' as reported by "
"the file system. (*since Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Het tijdstempel van het aanmaken van het bestand, zoals aangegeven door het "
"bestandssysteem, in de indeling ‘JJJJ-MM-DD UU:MM:SS’. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:45
msgid "**_file_modified_timestamp**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:47
msgid ""
"The file modification timestamp in the form 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS' as "
"reported by the file system. (*since Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Het tijdstempel van het bewerken van het bestand, zoals aangegeven door het "
"bestandssysteem, in de indeling ‘JJJJ-MM-DD UU:MM:SS’. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:49
msgid "**_format**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:51
msgid "Media format of the file (e.g.: MPEG-1 Audio)."
msgstr "De indeling van het bestand (bijv. MPEG-1-audio)."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:53
msgid "**_length**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:55
msgid "The length of the track in format mins:secs."
msgstr "De duur van het nummer, in de indeling min:s."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:57
msgid "**_sample_rate**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:59
msgid "Number of digitizing samples per second (Hz)."
msgstr "Het aantal digitale monsters per seconde (Hz)."

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:61
msgid "**_filesize**"
msgstr "**_filesize**"

#: ../../variables/variables_file.rst:63
msgid "Size of the file in bytes."
msgstr "De grootte van het bestand in bytes."
